5
00:00:36,578 --> 00:00:38,329
-Mom.
-[On-jo] Cheong-san, no.

6
00:00:45,545 --> 00:00:46,755
What the hell?

7
00:00:51,593 --> 00:00:52,927
-Damn it!
-[growls]

8
00:00:53,011 --> 00:00:54,179
[grunts]

9
00:00:54,929 --> 00:00:56,097
[grunts]

10
00:00:57,766 --> 00:00:59,225
