[Mi-jin] No! No, stop it!

599
00:40:21,293 --> 00:40:23,212
No! Wait!

600
00:40:23,838 --> 00:40:26,465
-I'm sorry!
-[groaning]

601
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:29,427
[screams]

602
00:40:37,476 --> 00:40:38,477
Push!

603
00:40:38,561 --> 00:40:39,812
[grunting]

